## ✨ Key Features

### 🔐 User Authentication
- Register and login with email
- Secure JWT-based session
- BCrypt password hashing

### 🗺️ Find Nearby Parking
- GPS-based location detection
- Color-coded map markers (green = available, red = occupied)
- Filter by distance and price

### ✅ Mark Availability (Crowd-sourced)
- Users update spot status in real time
- WebSocket push to all nearby users
- Availability log maintained for analytics

### 🔔 Notifications
- Alert when a nearby spot opens up
- Firebase Cloud Messaging integration
- In-app + push notifications

### 📅 Slot Reservation
- Pre-book parking slots in advance
- QR code generated for entry/exit scanning
- Automatic fee calculation

### 🤖 AI Prediction *(Advanced Feature)*
- ML-based availability forecasting
- Historical usage pattern analysis
- Peak hour heatmaps for better planning

